#: ../../../variable/CMAKE_TEST_BUILD_DEPENDS.rst:2
msgid "CMAKE_TEST_BUILD_DEPENDS"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../variable/CMAKE_TEST_BUILD_DEPENDS.rst:8
msgid ":generator:`FASTBuild` gained support for ``test_prep/<name>`` targets."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../variable/CMAKE_TEST_BUILD_DEPENDS.rst:10
msgid ""
"Enable ``test_prep/<name>`` build targets for tests added by :command:"
"`add_test` when using the :ref:`Ninja Generators` or :generator:`FASTBuild`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../variable/CMAKE_TEST_BUILD_DEPENDS.rst:14
msgid ""
"When this variable is set to a true value, CMake generates a ``test_prep/"
"<name>`` target for each eligible test and a ``test_prep/all`` target for "
"all such tests. Building these targets ensures the test executable, targets "
"referenced by test command generator expressions, and explicit "
"``BUILD_DEPENDS`` entries are up-to-date before the test runs."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../variable/CMAKE_TEST_BUILD_DEPENDS.rst:20
msgid ""
"Tests whose names are not valid target names are excluded from this "
"behavior. If multiple tests in different directories share the same name, "
"their dependencies are merged into a single ``test_prep/<name>`` target."
msgstr ""
